::DeathStorm::

DeathStorm falls forward and gets to his feet.

"I am not here to fight you..." He says cooly.

"I am ... Kluster," He says, remembering the name of a maximal he had once 
murdered, "A maximal fighter. I am here to help Liono Prime."
